#x0200a;0.35).</p><table-wrap id="pone-0041290-t008" orientation="portrait" position="float"><object-id pub-id-type="doi">10.1371/journal.pone.0041290.t008</object-id><label>Table 8</label><caption><title>Microbiology of pneumonia according to the treatment group.</title></caption><alternatives><graphic id="pone-0041290-t008-8" xlink:href="pone.0041290.t008"/><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><colgroup span="1"><col align="left" span="1"/><col align="center" span="1"/><col align="center" span="1"/><col align="center" span="1"/></colgroup><thead><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"/><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">15 days<xref ref-type="table-fn" rid="nt109">*</xref>
